Drop helios_plugin_cost_governor.wasm here.

Build with:
  cd ../../../../HDB-HeliosDB-Proxy-Plugins
  cargo build -p helios-plugin-cost-governor \
    --target wasm32-unknown-unknown --release
  cp target/wasm32-unknown-unknown/release/helios_plugin_cost_governor.wasm \
     /path/to/this/dir/

The demo.sh script does this automatically when invoked from a
checkout that has the plugins workspace at ../../../../.
